game_description: You can experience clay shooting sports in the western United States. I tried to apply a sense of reality to loading and shooting. If you hit the clay, coins will fall from the sky as a reward. Build coins like a mountain! A map against the backdrop of a modern clay shooting range will be applied. Thank you for waiting for further updates! - resource copyright list https://jeongday.notion.site/Clay-Shooter-Copyright-List-c102e36456584cd88290cf1b6300858f
